Achievements.Name: First Step
Achievements.Description: Win a fight in either Story mode or 1 Player Arcade mode.

Achievements.Name: Glory to Hiccup
Achievements.Description: Finish the Story mode with Hiccup.

Achievements.Name: Glory to Astrid
Achievements.Description: Finish the Story mode with Astrid.

Achievements.Name: Great Speaker
Achievements.Description: Talk to every person on the island in Story mode.

Achievements.Name: In Feathers
Achievements.Description: Catch 200 chickens.

Achievements.Name: More Wild Meat
Achievements.Description: Catch 200 sheep or boars.

Achievements.Name: New Champion
Achievements.Description: Win against the leader of the first Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Courageous
Achievements.Description: Win against the leader of the second Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Daring
Achievements.Description: Win against the leader of the third Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Fearless
Achievements.Description: Win against the leader of the fourth Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Unstoppable
Achievements.Description: Win the first Tournament without being defeated.

Achievements.Name: In Great Shape
Achievements.Description: Win the second Tournament without taking care of your dragons during it.

Achievements.Name: Valiant
Achievements.Description: Win the third Tournament always fighting the lowest rated opponent.

Achievements.Name: Brave
Achievements.Description: Win the fourth Tournament always fighting the highest rated opponent.

Achievements.Name: Invulnerable
Achievements.Description: Win the final Championship with none of your dragons being KO.

Achievements.Name: Weapon Master
Achievements.Description: Make a dragon finish all trainings.

Achievements.Name: Duelist
Achievements.Description: Win a wild fight.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Fighter
Achievements.Description: Win all wild fights.

Achievements.Name: Shopping Master
Achievements.Description: Spend 10,000 gold at the shop.

Achievements.Name: Cooking Master
Achievements.Description: Buy all recipes from the shop.

Achievements.Name: Rich Harvest
Achievements.Description: Gather 1,000 common ingredients.

Achievements.Name: Enlightened
Achievements.Description: Gather 100 rare ingredients.

Achievements.Name: Dragon Doctor
Achievements.Description: Have 4 dragons in a great shape in Story mode.

Achievements.Name: Final Evolution
Achievements.Description: Have a level 25 dragon.

Achievements.Name: All Stars
Achievements.Description: Have 4 level 25 dragons.

Achievements.Name: Belong to the Legend
Achievements.Description: Unlock all legendary dragons.

Achievements.Name: Perfectionist
Achievements.Description: Have a dragon with 20 points in a characteristic in Story mode.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Customization
Achievements.Description: Unlock all customizations of a dragon family.

Achievements.Name: Perfect
Achievements.Description: Win 50 fights without being injured in 1 Player Arcade mode.

Achievements.Name: Conqueror
Achievements.Description: Win 100 fights in either 1 Player or 2 Players Arcade mode.

Achievements.Name: Commander
Achievements.Description: Win 10 fights in a row in 1 Player Arcade mode on Hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: All for One
Achievements.Description: Win a fight with each default and Legendary dragons in 1 Player Arcade mode.

Achievements.Name: They Are Alive!
Achievements.Description: Win 20 fights in 1 Player Arcade mode with a team of dragons created with the Dragon Editor.

Achievements.Name: Exceptional Tamer
Achievements.Description: Win 20 fights in 1 Player Arcade mode with a team of custom dragons from the Story mode.

Achievements.Name: Game Over!
Achievements.Description: Win all the medals for all difficulty levels in each challenge.

Achievements.Name: Young Competitor
Achievements.Description: Earn a gold medal in any challenge on Novice difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Outstanding Competitor
Achievements.Description: Earn a gold medal in any challenge on Normal difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Extreme Competitor
Achievements.Description: Earn a gold medal in any challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: To Hit the Bull's Eyes
Achievements.Description: Clear 5 checkpoint rings in a row in the Looping Race challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: What an Artist!
Achievements.Description: Sculpt 10 ice blocks in a row in the Ice Sculpting challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Shepherd Dragon
Achievements.Description: Bring back 5 brown sheep in a row in the Flying Shepherd challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Brainy
Achievements.Description: Perform 6 sequences in a row in the Memory Torch challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Precise
Achievements.Description: Recreate 3 dragons in a row without mistakes in the Puzzle Dragon challenge on Expert difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Success
Achievements.Description: Earn a gold medal in each challenge.

Achievements.Name: Viking Gold
Achievements.Description: Have 10,000 gold in Story mode.

Achievements.Name: Viking Inhabitant
Achievements.Description: Play more than 20 hours in Story or Arcade mode (primary profile only).

Achievements.Name: Ally or Enemy?
Achievements.Description: Import at least one dragon in Arcade mode.
